narrowly tailored and really content, not content-based, just time of everyone had the same amount of time or could speak one time per meeting. The Swansea case involved a sufficiency of meeting notices, so I've included that. And the Boulder case probably isn't applicable to your commission, but certainly wanted to make sure you had all that information as well.

