89
00:36:58,452 --> 00:37:19,833
you would wanna take a break to try to fix the tech issue essentially, but continuing a meeting and posting a recording doesn't cure a violation. And so you really wanna make sure members of the public that are at home can certainly access the meeting in an accessible manner to allow them to follow along in real time.

90
00:37:24,811 --> 00:37:45,567
